# New First Post
#### 06-06-2021

A new first post is something I've written like a hundered times by now. Moving from handwritten html based websites to static site generators like @[jekyll](https://jekyllrb.com/), I've tried a lot of things. But I'm bored of writing out all that html by hand, and I need a break from my latest project. For these reasons, I've written a simple tool named @[lih](https://github.com/aelobdog/lih) to help in creating and maintaining this simple blog.

This site is powered by lih and another tool I wrote some time ago, @[sitefl](https://github.com/aelobdog/sitefl) . Sitefl is a markdown alternative which means just like when I was using Jekyll, I can write posts comfortably, with no need for any handwritten HTML.

Lih is not really meant to do a whole lot and there's probably a few bugs in it, so I'll try and fix them as and when I run into them 😁.
